WEBVTT

00:01.948 --> 00:03.983
It's so annoying, right?

00:04.050 --> 00:06.051
Yeah. They change the street-cleaning days,

00:06.119 --> 00:08.754
And no one tells you it's on Tuesday now.

00:08.822 --> 00:11.223
I got a $65 ticket.

00:11.291 --> 00:12.958
Yeah, I probably should fight it,

00:13.026 --> 00:14.394
But I mean, come on, who has time

00:14.461 --> 00:17.030
To take a half day off
and go to traffic court?

00:17.097 --> 00:20.600
all right, well,
I got to take a shower, so...

00:20.668 --> 00:23.336
We're still on for tonight, though, right?

00:23.404 --> 00:24.337
Okay.

00:24.405 --> 00:27.073
Yep, I will see you then. Bye.

00:28.776 --> 00:31.644
Well... Looks like it's
your lucky day, jinx.

00:31.712 --> 00:34.914
I am all out of dry food.

00:36.483 --> 00:38.284
Oh.

00:38.352 --> 00:39.385
Hello?

00:39.453 --> 00:40.520
Naomi?

00:40.587 --> 00:43.089
Uh, no, I'm sorry, this is gretchen.

00:43.157 --> 00:45.658
Oh. I'm sorry.

00:45.726 --> 00:46.959
Is naomi there?

00:47.027 --> 00:49.429
Uh, no, there's no one named naomi here,

00:49.496 --> 00:52.098
So, um, I think you have the wrong number.

00:52.166 --> 00:53.166
Really?

00:53.233 --> 00:54.467
No, she has to be.

00:54.535 --> 00:56.069
She waited on me the other night,

00:56.136 --> 00:57.837
And we kind of hit it off.

00:57.905 --> 00:59.372
This is the number she gave me.

00:59.440 --> 01:02.408
Yeah, well, I'm sorry to be
the one to break it to you,

01:02.476 --> 01:05.311
But I think maybe this naomi,
whoever she is,

01:05.379 --> 01:07.847
She might not want to actually talk to you,

01:07.915 --> 01:10.016
So... Sorry. Bye.

01:10.084 --> 01:13.086
All right, jinx, chow time.

01:13.153 --> 01:14.620
Hop to it.

01:15.656 --> 01:17.290
Lazy dog.

01:20.594 --> 01:21.594
Hello?

01:21.662 --> 01:23.429
Okay, here's the thing.

01:23.497 --> 01:25.131
I know naomi's there,

01:25.199 --> 01:27.934
So stop playing around
and let me talk to her.

01:28.001 --> 01:30.036
Wow, you've really got a problem.

01:30.104 --> 01:32.138
Now, listen to me, okay?

01:32.206 --> 01:34.006
There is no naomi here,

01:34.074 --> 01:36.275
There are no waitresses that live here,

01:36.343 --> 01:39.312
And there is no one here
that wants to talk to you.

01:39.380 --> 01:41.447
Yes, there is... 

01:43.650 --> 01:45.651
Hey. Up and at 'em.

01:50.023 --> 01:51.624
Oh, my god.

01:51.692 --> 01:52.959
Jinx?

01:59.833 --> 02:01.834
Oh, my god...

02:03.070 --> 02:04.203
Hello?

02:04.271 --> 02:07.006
Tell that bitch naomi to come to the phone.

02:07.074 --> 02:08.640
Oh, no. No, no, no, no.

02:08.709 --> 02:09.976
Stop calling me, okay?

02:10.043 --> 02:11.878
I can't deal with you right now.

02:11.945 --> 02:13.246
I have an emergency.

02:13.313 --> 02:17.650
A dead dog is not an emergency.

02:18.819 --> 02:20.820
Who is this?

02:23.357 --> 02:24.924
Okay... 

02:24.992 --> 02:26.993
I'm gonna go get your... Your pen,

02:27.060 --> 02:29.362
A-and I'm taking you to the vet.

